Who Do You Think You Are? Australia - Series 7, Episode 3




Luke Nguyen

Chef and restaurateur Luke Nguyen was born in 1978 into a world of danger and uncertainty - his family was among the two million Vietnamese who fled the Communist regime after the Vietnam War. While the Nguyen family eventually found safety, settling in Cabramatta, Sydney - their life in Australia was anything but easy.




Original Air Date: 18-Aug-2015
